gov.usgs.anss.cwbqueryclient

Class MSOutputer

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.anss.cwbqueryclient.Outputer
      • gov.usgs.anss.cwbqueryclient.MSOutputer

  • public class MSOutputer
extends Outputer
    Create a simple miniSEED file from the CWBQuery list of miniSEED blocks. This allows options for setting the filename with "-o", eliminating dups in the data, forcing the network code. Notice dups are normally not present in the list as CWBQuery normally would suppress them.

        Parameters:
        comp - NNSSSSSCCCLL channel name
        filename - Filename for output
        filemask - The file mask with % operators for constructing a name (filename was derived from this)

        beg - The beginning time of the time series
